hy nwnk! jo mnu`K gurU dy khy qy qurdw hY auh (ivkwrW dI) mwr nhIN KWdw ]35]
jo mnu`K gurU dy d`sy rwh qy qurdw hY, aus dw nwm jpxw dwn krnw qy ieSnwn krnw pRvwn hY[
gurU dy snmuK hoieAW hI Afol AvsQw ivc surq juVdI hY[
jo mnu`K gurU dy snmuK hY auh pRBU dI hzUrI ivc Awdr pWdw hY[
auh aus pRBU nUM iml pYNdw hY jo fr-sihm nws krn vwlw hY qy jo sB dw mwlk hY[
gurmuK mnu`K (hornW pwsoN BI iehI, Bwv, gurU dy hukm ivc qurn vwlw) krn-jog kMm krWdw hY,
(qy ies qrHW auhnW nUM) hy nwnk! (pRBU dy) myl ivc imlw dyNdw hY ]36]
jo mnu`K gurU dy d`sy rwh qy qurdw hY, auh (mwno) SwsqRW isimRqIAW qy vydW dw igAwn hwsl kr cukw hY, (Bwv, gurU dy hukm ivc qurnw hI gurmuiK leI vydW SwsqRW qy isimRqIAW dw igAwn hY)[
