hy nwnk! gurU dy snmuK mnu`K ny Ksm (-pRBU) nUM pCwx ilAw hY ]37]
siqgurU (dI srn Awaux) qoN ibnw (mnu`K mwieAw ivc) Btkdw hY qy jMmdw mrdw rihMdw hY[
gur-srx qoN ibnw koeI myhnq kbUl nhIN pYNdI (ikauNik "hau" itkI rihMdI hY)[
siqgurU qoN ibnw ieh cMcl mn bhuq sNhisAW ivc rihMdw hY,
siqgurU qoN ibnw ieh zihr Kw Kw ky (Bwv dunIAw dy pdwrQ mwx mwx ky) r`jIdw nhIN[
gurU (dy rwh qy qurn) qoN ibnw (jgq dw moh-rUp) s`p fMg mwrdw rihMdw hY, (izMdgI dy s&r dy) A`D ivc hI (Awqmk mOqy) mrIdw hY[
hy nwnk! siqgurU dy (hukm ivc qurn) qoN ibnw mnu`K nUM (Awqmk jIvn ivc) Gwtw hI Gwtw rihMdw hY ]38]
ijs mnu`K nUM siqgur iml pYNdw hY aus nUM (auh "duqr swgr" qoN) pwr lMGw lYNdw hY,
gurU aus dy Aaugx imtw dyNdw hY qy gux dy ky aus nUM (ivkwrW qoN) bcw lYNdw hY[
siqgurU dw Sbd ivcwr ky aus nUM (mwieAw dy bMDnW qoN) AwzwdI dw v`fw suK imldw hY[
jo mnu`K gurU dy snmuK (hY auh izMdgI dI bwzI kdy) hwr ky nhIN AwauNdw[
