hy nwnk! Afolqw ivc rih ky prmwqmw dw nwm-vxj krdw hY ]39]
krqwr ny (sMswr-smuMdr qy) gurmuiK-rUp pul bMnH id`qw (ijvyN rwmcMdR jI ny sIqw nUM ilAwaux vwsqy smuMdr qy pul b`Dw sI)[
(rwmcMdR jI ny) lMkw lu`tI qy rwKS mwry, (iqvyN gurU ny kwmwidkW dy v`s ivc pey srIr nUM auhnW qoN Cufw ilAw qy auh pMj dUq v`s ivc ho gey)[
rwmcMdR (jI) ny rwvx nUM mwirAw iqvyN gurmuK ny mn-s`p nUM mwr id`qw;
siqgurU dw aupdyS (mn nUM mwrn ivc ieauN kMm AwieAw ijvyN) bBIKx dw Byq d`sxw (rwvx nUM mwrn leI kMm AwieAw)[
